15 (b) For purposes of this Code section, nontax related fees or assessments shall include, but
16 shall not be limited to, storm-water service fees; solid waste service fees; fees for water and
17 waste water; and any late fees, penalties, or interest related to anything other than the ad
18 valorem taxes on the real property itself. Any collection and any payment of such nontax
19 related fees or assessments shall be addressed in billings separate from bills or assessments
20 for the collection and payment of ad valorem taxes on real property.
21 (c) For purposes of this Code section, nontax related fees or assessments shall not include
22 any fee, assessment, charge, or cost related to delinquent ad valorem property tax
23 collections, including, but not limited to, any delinquent ad valorem property tax collection
24 costs allowed pursuant to Title 15 or 48.
25 (d) This Code section shall be applicable to all bills and assessments issued on or after
26 January 1, 2026."
27 SECTION 2.
28 All laws and parts of laws in conflict with this Act are repealed.
